        "subject": "LU-2748 Allocate struct osd_thread_info with vmalloc",
        "message": "LU-2748 Allocate struct osd_thread_info with vmalloc\n\nNeed to allocate struct osd_thread_info in osd_key_init with\nOBD_ALLOC_LARGE, since otherwise we get order 5 allocation which\nis hard to fulfil.\nThis is mostly a bandaid before we get around to actually splitting\nthat allocation into better sized smaller pieces on as needed basis.\n\nChange-Id: Id9cabab488c5651c2cc14ac7576961fda4c54c5e\nSigned-off-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
